---

<Layout
  title="Handyman Decatur AL | Drywall, Painting & Gutters | Rittenworx"
  description="Licensed handyman in Decatur, AL — drywall, painting, flooring, carpentry & gutters. Serving downtown Decatur, Point Mallard & Somerville. Free written estimates."
  schema={pageSchema}
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-blue-900 text-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <nav class="text-sm text-blue-200 mb-4">
          <a href="/locations" class="hover:text-white">Service Areas</a>
          <span class="mx-2">/</span>
          <span class="text-white">Decatur</span>
        </nav>
        <span
          class="text-orange-400 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wide"
          >City Hub</span
        >
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mt-2 mb-4">
          Decatur's Handyman Contractor Who Works Around Your Shift Schedule
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-blue-100 mb-6">
          Daikin, 3M, Nucor — we know Decatur runs on rotating shifts. We schedule
          around yours, communicate by text, and don't expect you to answer calls
          at 10 AM when you're sleeping before a night shift. Quick scheduling
          across Morgan County. Written estimates. Licensed and insured.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="bg-orange-500 hover:bg-orange-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition-colors"
          >
            Get Free Estimate
          </a>
          <a
            href="tel:2562210373"
            class="bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition-colors"
          >
            (256) 221-0373
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Quick Stats -->
  <section class="bg-white py-8 border-b">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 text-center">
        <div>
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-900">On Time</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Service in Decatur</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-900">Morgan Co.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Full Coverage</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-900">57,000+</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Decatur Residents</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-900">Free</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Estimates Always</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Communities We Serve -->
  <section class="py-8 bg-blue-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-4">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800">
          Decatur Area Communities:
        </h2>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a
            href="/locations/decatur/somerville"
            class="bg-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow text-blue-900 font-medium flex items-center gap-2"
          >
            Somerville
            <svg
              class="w-4 h-4"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <span class="bg-gray-100 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-gray-600"
            >Priceville</span
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Decatur Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <span
            class="text-orange-700 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wide"
            >The River City</span
          >
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mt-2 mb-6">
            Decatur Homeowners Who Expect Precision — We Match That Standard
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            The people who build HVAC systems at Daikin, pour steel at Nucor,
            and manufacture rocket components at United Launch Alliance hold
            their work to exacting standards. They tend to hold their home
            contractors to the same bar. We're fine with that.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            We've been committing to Decatur the same way we commit to Madison
            — regular weekly jobs, not occasional drive-bys. We know the river
            humidity accelerates exterior wear faster than anywhere else in the
            Valley. We know Old Decatur's Victorian homes need restoration, not
            just repair. We know the difference between the two.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            $1M liability coverage. Written estimates that don't change.
            availability for most Morgan County areas. Free estimate — call
            (256) 221-0373 or get your quote online.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4">
            Decatur Quick Facts
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            {
              decaturFacts.map((fact) => (
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg
                    class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  >
                    <path
                      stroke-linecap="round"
                      stroke-linejoin="round"
                      stroke-width="2"
                      d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"
                    />
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">{fact}</span>
                </li>
              ))
            }
          </ul>
          <div class="mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-gray-200">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">
              River Humidity Changes the Timeline
            </h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
              Paint that lasts 8–10 years elsewhere lasts 5–7 near the river.
              Deck stains fail faster. Caulk around windows deteriorates sooner.
              We factor that in — your maintenance schedule should too.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Elevated Direct Response: Decatur Home Intelligence -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">
          The River City Factor: Why Decatur Homes Need More Maintenance Than You Expect
        </h2>
        <p>
          If you moved to Decatur from elsewhere in North Alabama, here's
          something most contractors won't tell you: the river changes the
          timeline on everything exterior. Humidity from the Tennessee River
          basin infiltrates wood, paint, caulk joints, and gutters in ways that
          inland homeowners simply don't deal with.
        </p>
        <p>
          The numbers are real. Exterior paint that lasts 8–10 years in a
          typical Madison neighborhood lasts 5–7 near the river. Deck stains
          fail faster. Caulk around windows and doors deteriorates sooner.
          Gutters corrode earlier. None of that is speculation — it's what
          happens when you put materials in a subtropical river climate.
          Catching it on the front end costs hundreds. Ignoring it costs
          thousands.
        </p>
        <p>
          Then there are the shift schedules. Workers at Daikin, 3M, and Nucor
          don't keep 9-to-5 hours. Someone may be sleeping at 10 AM and leaving
          for a night shift at 2 PM. We work around that. We schedule to your
          availability, communicate by text, and don't expect you to answer a
          call during sleep hours. Most contractors from Huntsville won't bother
          — Decatur is a 30-minute drive and an afterthought to them.
          It's a regular part of our weekly schedule.
        </p>
        <p>
          Old Decatur's Victorian homes add one more layer. Victorian-era
          construction used materials and techniques most modern contractors
          have never encountered. Original plaster responds differently than
          drywall. Period trim profiles need custom matching, not off-the-shelf
          replacement. We know the difference between restoration and
          remodeling — and we know which one you need. Free estimate.
          Written quote. Call (256) 221-0373 or get your estimate online — we
          get back to you quickly.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Neighborhoods Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span
          class="text-orange-700 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wide"
          >Neighborhood Coverage</span
        >
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mt-2">
          Decatur Neighborhoods We Serve
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          From riverfront historic districts to growing suburban communities, we
          serve every corner of Decatur and Morgan County.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        {
          neighborhoods.map((neighborhood) => (
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-5 border-2 border-gray-100 hover:border-blue-200 transition-colors">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                <h3 class="text-md font-bold text-blue-900">
                  {neighborhood.name}
                </h3>
              </div>
              <span class="text-xs bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-2 py-1 rounded-full">
                {neighborhood.responseTime}
              </span>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-3 mb-3">
                {neighborhood.description}
              </p>
              <div>
                <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase mb-2">
                  Common Services
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1">
                  {neighborhood.commonServices.slice(0, 3).map((service) => (
                    <span class="text-xs bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 px-2 py-1 rounded">
                      {service}
                    </span>
                  ))}
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Response Times -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-blue-900 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Response Times for Decatur Areas</h2>
        <p class="text-blue-100 mt-4">
          Just 30 minutes via I-565, we reach all Decatur neighborhoods
          efficiently.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        {
          responseTimes.map((item) => (
            <div class="bg-white/10 rounded-lg p-4 flex items-center justify-between">
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold">{item.area}</p>
              </div>
              <span
                class={`px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium ${
                  item.time === "Quick scheduling"
                    ? "bg-green-500 text-white"
                    : "bg-yellow-500 text-black"
                }`}
              >
                {item.time}
              </span>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>
      <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <p class="text-blue-100">
          Serving all Decatur areas. Call or text to get on the
          repairs.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Weather Challenges -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span
          class="text-orange-700 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wide"
          >River City Expertise</span
        >
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mt-2">
          Decatur Weather Challenges
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Decatur's Tennessee River location creates specific climate
          challenges. We understand how river valley weather affects your home.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        {
          weatherChallenges.map((weather) => (
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                  {weather.season.includes("Spring") && (
                    <svg
                      class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600"
                      fill="none"
                      stroke="currentColor"
                      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    >
                      <path
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"
                      />
                    </svg>
                  )}
                  {weather.season.includes("Summer") && (
